sourcesContent:
import { Header } from '../../section/index'

import { Card , Container , Button} from '../../components/index'
export default function About() {
  return (
    <>

      
      <Container>
      <Card 
        title='Mission'
        img='../../assets/images/mission.png'
        soustitle='Support the strategy of job creation by incentivizing youth to provide digital services fundamentally to create a contextual platform.'
        
      />
      <Card 
        title='Vision'
        image='../../assets/images/vision.png'
        soustitle=
        'Revitalize the Lebanese economy by job creation and disseminating digital services.'
        
      />
      <Card 
        title=' Values'
        image='../../assets/images/values.png'
        soustitle='· Accountability
        · Affordability
        · Authenticity
        · Commitment
        · Integrity
        · Transparency
        · Flexibility
        · Empowerment
        · Professionalism
        · Sustainability'
      />
      </Container>
      <Button text='Start Your Project'/>
    </>
  )
}
